paragraphs.text:
%sql

SELECT rating, COUNT(*) AS count FROM ratings GROUP BY rating

final case class Movie(movieId: Int, title: String)

def mapperMovies(line: String) = {
    val fields = line.split('|')
    Movie(fields(0).toInt, fields(1))
}

val movies = sc.textFile("/data/ml-100k/u.item").map(mapperMovies)

import sqlContext.implicits._

val moviesDF = movies.toDF

moviesDF.printSchema

moviesDF.show(10)
